{"tid":492255,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"上古卷軸ONLINE 又半價","createTime":"2017-12-07T10:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T12:29:46.000Z","uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3ff25c9b936a99b19d9ae4c4f4a6850932b300c0","tid":492255,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:57:03.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">The elder scrolls online (ESO)</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<img src=\"http://i1-news.softpedia-static.com/images/news2/The-Elder-Scrolls-Online-May-Become-Free-to-Play-in-Less-Than-6-Months-Report-468693-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1-news.softpedia-static.com%2Fimages%2Fnews2%2FThe-Elder-Scrolls-Online-May-Become-Free-to-Play-in-Less-Than-6-Months-Report-468693-2.jpg&h=d1c27cee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>ESO普遍問題Q&amp;A</strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">Q:乜L野係eso,新game黎?</span></strong><br />\nA:《上古卷軸Online》（The Elder Scrolls Online）是一款大型多人線上角色扮演遊戲，由ZeniMax Online Studios研發製作，貝塞斯達軟件發行，並在2014年4月4日於Microsoft Windows和OS X平台上發行，而PlayStation 4和Xbox One版本在2015年6月9日推出。本作屬於《上古卷軸》電子遊戲系列，也是該系列中第一款開放結局的多人遊戲作品。(wiki jj)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Q:ESO要點樣買?</strong></span></span><br />\nA:以<span style=\"color: red;\">Steam</span>為平台<br />\nThe Elder Scrolls&reg; Online: Tamriel Unlimited(<strong>only本體)</strong><br />\n<br />\nThe Elder Scrolls Online - Morrowind(<strong>本體+晨風DLC</strong>)<br />\n<br />\nThe Elder Scrolls Online - Morrowind - Digital Collector's Edition(<strong>上面既土豪版</strong>)<br />\n<br />\nThe Elder Scrolls&reg; Online: Gold Edition(<strong>本體+4個DLC,<span style=\"color: gold;\">黄金版</span></strong>)<br />\n<br />\n一般新手推薦入<span style=\"color: gold;\">黄金版</span>,不過既有sale既話就隨便你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">Q:eso同skyrim係咪同一隻game既online版?</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nA:NO,ESO同skyrim完全唔同,ー隻係onlineRPG,另一隻係PC單機game,只係時空背景ー樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">Q:eso有咩ser可以玩?PC,xbox,ps4又可唔可以一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong><br />\n<br />\nA:NA(北美)同EU(歐洲)兩個ser,呢到絶大多數人係NA,人都比EU多,ping比EU低<br />\nPC,xbox,ps4<span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以</span>一齊玩,大家都係<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立ser</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Q:eso其實係玩D乜,同skyrim之前D系列有咩分別?</strong></span><br />\nA:ESO簡單黎講一樣係打任,打副本,刷裝,loop,不過今次你唔再孤單,亦唔駛對著Ai隊友自言自語,因為有你有我有大家一齊面對塔姆瑞爾既危機<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但同你以前玩開既rpggame唔同係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">劇情非常非常豐富</span></strong>,<br />\nESO可以行遍成個塔姆瑞爾大陸,而skyrim局限係天際同索瑟姆,所以係非常噤玩<br />\n[b]<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上次開POST好多巴打加入左"},{"pid":"21d9595a1f2bbe51434972bd09ff153890fecad9","tid":492255,"uid":134255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T11:14:08.000Z","msg":"駛唔駛另俾月費？"},{"pid":"127136215b3fe589404e0820036cc8a220acb181","tid":492255,"uid":134255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T11:16:27.000Z","msg":"仲想問ps4 有冇中文版"},{"pid":"85c33a3bae5dd8759797a2fd2c484df36b7651c8","tid":492255,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T11:29:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>駛唔駛另俾月費？</blockquote><br />\n唔駛"},{"pid":"3eb2fce65ff1da7c436c84e202d0934d02edcc93","tid":492255,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T11:29:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲想問ps4 有冇中文版</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif